Results.ReviewText: I use this coffee all the time and never tell friends it is caffeine free. Some of them have asked what kind of coffee it is as they have enjoyed it so much. Some have said that they were amazed as they thought that caffeine free coffee would not taste as good as their usual coffee with caffeine.
Results.Title: Can't tell the difference

Results.ReviewText: When visiting a friends office, I always make myself a coffee in their canteen. I never noticed I was using Nescafé Decaf ( I don't like decaf) but commenting on the great flavour I was informed She had changed to decaffinated "as it suited her better". Maybe I'll change a habit of a lifetime.
Results.Title: Didn't realise it was decaf

ClientResponses.Response: Thanks for the feedback! We're sad to hear you weren't a fan of NESCAFÉ Original Decaff but we hope you continue to enjoy NESCAFÉ Gold Blend Decaff.

Results.ReviewText: We tasted Nescafe's Original Decaff Coffee and found it tasty but too harsh and roasted a little too much for our palate.  Our preference is still Nescafe Gold Blend Decaff.  We appreciate the fact that most local suppliers stock Decaff and the constant smooth, tasteful flavour of our choice!
Results.Title: Two Tasters

Results.ReviewText: I decided to 'go' decaf about 4yrs ago and after sampling loads of brands I had to come to Nescafe Decaff as my choice. The decision was simple as Nescafe was a smooth,refreshing coffee that didn't leave a harsh aftertaste, in fact I've converted all friends to drink Nescafe Decaff as well.
Results.Title: The smoothest decaff out there

Results.ReviewText: After being told to drink decaf coffee I didn't think it would have the same flavour as my original Nescafé I was used to. I love it and haven't looked back since! It's full of its original flavour and it lasts much longer than any other coffee does. Same great taste and no more headaches!
Results.Title: Full of flavour

Results.ReviewText: For many years I have preferred decaf and Nescafe is by far the best I have tried.  I mix a spoonful with a little cooled boiled water and then top with skimmed milk I have frothed in my husband's aeroccino at a fraction of the cost of decaf pods and I defy anyone to say it's not as good.
Results.Title: Full of flavour

Results.ReviewText: Nothing like the 'original'. I enjoy the smooth taste, it is'nt bitter like some coffee's I have when out. The first thing I have in the morning is a coffee ( lovingly made by my husband) and I can start the day ready to go.I do prefer the de-caff and take it on holiday when we go away.
Results.Title: smooth and tasty

Results.ReviewText: As part of a healthier lifestyle I am reducing my intake of caffeine. I was recommended by a friend to try Nescafé de-caff and was pleasently surprised by the full flavour and now when I have a instant coffee I reach for the little blue jar and enjoy my cup of caffeine free coffee.
Results.Title: Tastes as great as Nescafé original

Results.ReviewText: I have used nescafe decaff for some time now at home and thought it was about time I introduced my friends in work to it. So I became the coffee monitor!!! and now all 10 of us drink only decaff. As we are all female, it has certainly helped our sensitive bladders!!  thanks nescafe
Results.Title: great tasting decaff

Results.ReviewText:
Lovely decaf coffee. The smell when opening the jar makes my mouth water. Very rich aroma. Lovely smooth taste, made extra special by being decaf, which means I can enjoy a milky coffee before bed. 
No difference in taste, smell or texture between the decaf and original. Lovely.
Results.Title: Lovely and smooth

Results.ReviewText: This is a go to decaff coffee. Easy to drink anytime - especially when you just fancy that fresh coffee flavor at night - without interfering with your sleep. Although its mega delicious it does not completely fulfill the perfect fresh cup flavor - but it more then hits the spot!
Results.Title: delicious easy flavor

Results.ReviewText: I have changed from my regular brand to try Nescafe Decaff and have been very surprised as the smoothness and lovely flavour of this coffee, I will certainly keep using this, my friends didnt even know it was Decaff when served to them as they thought it had a very rich taste
Results.Title: Smooth Taste

Results.ReviewText: Find the decaf coffee tasty and refreshing, being alergic to cafine I always purchse decaf coffee and have found the Nescafe origional good value and excellent taste. I particularly like to add a small shot of sugar free vanilla syrup which I feel really enhances the taste.
Results.Title: Great Value Product

Results.ReviewText: I bought this coffee to try as a morning drink as caffeine gives me terrible headaches, and this is perfect! The taste of the coffee is exactly the same as the original version and also makes me feel so much more awake. I do enjoy Nescafé products, and this is my favourite.
Results.Title: Perfect wake up in the morning!

Results.ReviewText: i started to buy this for my mum in law who has bladder probs and was told coffee was a no go so i did some research and seems decaf is ok, tried several brands and nothing came close to the rich smooth flavour of Nescafe Decaf  without losing any taste of the normal one.
Results.Title: Smooth and actually a health benefit!

Results.ReviewText: I recently decided to give try and cut down on my caffeine intake so bought a jar of nescafe as it was on offer at the local supermarket.  I was really surprised at how nice it was, I can't tell the difference and not missing my usual morning cup of caffeinated nescafe!
Results.Title: Tastes a good as the original

Results.ReviewText: Always swap to decaf after around 7pm so as I'm not kept awake at night. The taste is smooth and just as delicious as the Original blend. I like my coffee to taste of coffee but not be too bitter. Nescafe Decaf ticks all the boxes. Would certainly recommend the product.
Results.Title: You Won't Notice it Missing

Results.ReviewText: It is the best instant coffee full of flavour and useful to have sachets etc although I often have difficulty obtaining these.  For improvement I would suggest that the actual  quantity of caffeine  contained in an average cup would be advisable on the ingredients list.
Results.Title: Well known and reliable

Results.ReviewText: We tried decaff for the first time last month and we are wondering why we didn't swap sooner. It tastes no different to the normal coffee. I wouldn't know it was decaff and we won't be swapping back. Feel great after a mug of decaff and ready to take on the day ahead.
Results.Title: cant go wrong. simple which is great

Results.ReviewText: I have been using this for months in the afternoons and at bedtime in order to help me get a better nights sleep, and it works. It's much lighter than some other bedtime drinks and tastes just as good as filter coffee. My sleep has improved and I feel more refreshed.
Results.Title: Tastes just like original

Results.ReviewText: A friend gave me cup of the decaff and I couldn't believe it was decaff. I have been trying to convert to decaff to cut down my caffeine intake. The coffee tasted like a proper roasted bean coffee and very flavoursome . Would recommend as an excellent instant coffee.
Results.Title: I can't believe it's not Caffianted!

Results.ReviewText: I have been drinking Nescafé Decaff for many years and have never found another brand to match its taste. I stock up on jars when I see it on offer as this makes it very good value for money. I get through many jars as I love the smooth taste of this quality product.
Results.Title: Mellow taste

Results.ReviewText: I have been buying the decaf brand for a while, husband was not so keen but his converted him, he has realised the flavour are the same excellent taste, the only thing is the price wish it was a bit cheaper but in comparison to other brands I can't complain too much.
Results.Title: Excellent flavour

Results.ReviewText:
I always buy Original (Decaffeinated) Because I need a Caffeine free Coffee with Great Taste, and because Original Decaff is made from Medium Roasted Beans it satisfy my needs completely.

My slogan when looking for Coffee: -
"Why Bother - When there is No Other".
Results.Title: Fantastic Taste

Results.ReviewText: I used to drink regular Nescafé coffee but decided to try to be a bit healthier by drinking Nescafé decaf. Why didn't I do it sooner? - I can't tell the difference in taste but I find I sleep better and have fewer headaches. Keep up the good work Nescafé, thank you!
Results.Title: Can't tell the difference

Results.ReviewText: I bought this in desperation after the disappearance of your Alta Rica decaf (which is about the best on the market) - the Original is just not in the same universe! It's adequate and obviously significantly cheaper but not great. (Please bring back the AR decaf!)
Results.Title: Sorry!

Results.ReviewText: I love strong, robust coffee that has a smooth finish but I don't like being kept awake all night with a big caffeine hit.  Nescafe original decaff delivers on flavour and smoothness and lets me sleep soundly at night - everything you could ask of a decaff coffee
Results.Title: Strength without bitterness

Results.ReviewText: Tried the decaff at work totally by accident. Didn't look too closely at the label. It was only later a colleague told me there was only decaff available that day. No difference in taste to me at all. Drinking one of each in turn now to limit my caffeine intake!
Results.Title: No diff decaff

Results.ReviewText: Originally drank Nescafé Halfcaf which was just what I needed before I could switch totally to decaf.  Nescafé obviously thought about everything as I never saw halfcaf from other brands. I am now totally decaffinated thanks to Nescafé and I have been for years
Results.Title: Triangle

Results.ReviewText: Nescafe decaff has the same brilliant taste as the caffeinated version. When staying away overnight I take some with me along with some fresh cold milk in a small vacuum flask. If its a good hotel and they have Nescafe sachets I collect some for the next time.
Results.Title: Brilliant taste.

40640e88-8830-4a94-b793-8445e685a1d5.Description: Relax with a delicious decaff instant coffee, with NESCAFÉ Original Decaff. Enjoy its great full-flavoured taste, whenever you fancy a break.
40640e88-8830-4a94-b793-8445e685a1d5.Name: Nescafé Original Decaff

Results.Description: A well-rounded, smooth coffee with a rich aroma.
